worth everything in the world.

00:20:35.060 --> 00:20:37.320
Sometimes they take on the
appearance of statesmen

00:20:37.320 --> 00:20:38.860
and sometimes of sophists.

00:20:38.860 --> 00:20:40.900
Sometimes, too, they
