This is actually a direct quote.

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:46.280
It comes from "The Sophist."

00:20:46.280 --> 00:20:47.470
McCoy.

00:20:47.470 --> 00:20:49.640
"Well, I'm going to
go with that last one,

00:20:49.640 --> 00:20:52.340
