00:21:11.780 --> 00:21:16.390
whether or not there can be
morality without religion?

00:21:16.390 --> 00:21:19.560
Has science progressed?

00:21:19.560 --> 00:21:22.610
Roy McCoy doesn't even think
science has progressed,

00:21:22.610 --> 00:21:24.212
much less philosophy.

00:21:24.212 --> 00:21:25.920
And one of the things
