one is the head

00:22:44.840 --> 00:22:48.760
of the laboratory,
Dr. Shokett-- one

00:22:48.760 --> 00:22:53.350
whether or not neuroscience has
retired many of the questions

00:22:53.350 --> 00:22:56.390
