used to lay claim

00:22:56.390 --> 00:23:00.750
to, free will,
personal identity?

00:23:00.750 --> 00:23:07.190
And in fact, all notions of a
person choosing their own life,

00:23:07.190 --> 00:23:10.720
making choices,
decisions intentions?

00:23:10.720 --> 00:23:14.690
And standards of rationality,
whether it's all determined

00:23:14.690 --> 00:23:20.690
and its determined on the
level of our 100 billion

00:23:20.690 --> 00:23:24.330
neurons firing, or
100 trillion synapses?

00:23:24.330 --> 00:23:28.020
Plato, by this time, knows
a lot of neuroscience.

00:23:28.020 --> 00:23:32.380
And he has a discussion with
these two neuroscientists

00:23:32.380 --> 00:23:33.090
there.

00:23:33.090 --> 00:23:35.969
Anyway, so those are
