what they called "kleos"

00:27:11.640 --> 00:27:15.430
and what we might call
a high Klout score.

00:27:15.430 --> 00:27:20.270
And one of the ways in which
we're very close to them.

00:27:20.270 --> 00:27:21.580
And they flocked to this.

00:27:21.580 --> 00:27:24.680
And Plato gave this talk
on "The Good," which

00:27:24.680 --> 00:27:31.920
